message.body: Hello, dear cousin. Are you going to be in New Ulm next week?
Alas not reallllllly. But I can be in northfield and meet you halfway and that's where tye will be
An hour south of the cities and an hour and a half away from new ulm
Okay. Then I will come to Northfield. My dad is heading to New Ulm on Tues-Fri, so I have to visit new ulm at some point.
Oh whatever works best for you. And ask tye about logistics bc it's his house and all
Okay. Visiting your brother for a bit?
Yea I'd come down to see you guys. He lives there and I live in mpls.
